<main id="main">
    @* <section> *@
    <div class="container-fluid">
        <h1 class="text-center pt-5 ">
            Ticket Management Application
        </h1><hr />
        <div style="border:3px solid Black; height:600px;" class=" mt-4"><img src="~/images/Portfolio/TicketManagementApp/Ticket Management.png" alt="Ticket Management" title="Ticket Management" loading="lazy" class="img-fluid w-100 h-100 d-block img-thumbnail"/></div>
    </div>
    <div class="container-fluid mt-3">
        <div class="row mt-5 mx-2">
            <div class="col-lg-9 p-3 mt-4 d-flex flex-column justify-content-center align-items-center" style="background-color:aliceblue">
                <div class="mt-4 p-3 mb-4 bg-white">
                    <h4 class="mt-4 m-3">Overview</h4>
                    <p class="m-3">
                        The Ticket Management Application built using Power Apps streamlines the process of managing support or service tickets within an organization. This app offers an intuitive interface, seamless integration with SharePoint, and customizable features for handling ticket creation, updates, and tracking. It is ideal for organizations seeking an efficient solution for ticket lifecycle management.
                    </p>
                    <h5 class="mt-4 m-3">Key Features:-</h5>
                    <h6 class="m-3">1. Home Screen:-</h6>
                    <p class="m-3">For showing all the tickets.</p>
                    <h6 class="m-3">2. Dynamic Filters :-</h6>
                    <p class="m-3">Filters allow users to quickly view specific ticket types:</p>
                    <ul class="m-3">
                        <li>All Tickets</li>
                        <li>New Tickets</li>
                        <li>Tickets in Progress</li>
                        <li>Tickets On Hold</li>
                        <li>Tickets Closed</li>
                        <li>Tickets Older than 3 Days</li>
                        <li>Tickets Opened Today</li>
                        <li>Tickets Closed Today</li>
                    </ul>
                    <h6 class="m-3">3. Create New Ticket Screen</h6>
                    <img src="~/images/Portfolio/ticketmanagementapp/New Ticket Screen.png" alt="New Ticket Screen" title="New Ticket Screen" loading="lazy" class="img-fluid w-100 img-thumbnail rounded mx-auto d-block" />
                    <h5 class="mt-4 m-3">Ticket Details Screen</h5>
                    <p class="m-3">Displays detailed ticket information:</p>
                    <img src="~/images/Portfolio/ticketmanagementapp/Ticket Details Screen.png" alt="Ticket Details Screen" title="Ticket Details Screen" loading="lazy" class="img-fluid w-100 img-thumbnail rounded mx-auto d-block" />
                    <hr />
                    <h5 class="mt-4 m-3">Benefits</h5>
                    <ul class="m-3">
                        <li>Streamlined Workflow: Simplifies ticket management with an easy-to-use interface.</li>
                        <li>Dynamic Filters: Quickly sort and find relevant tickets.</li>
                        <li>Customizable: Adapts to specific organizational needs.</li>
                        <li>Seamless Integration: Leverages SharePoint for efficient data handling.</li>
                        <li>Improved Tracking: Detailed ticket information ensures better follow-ups.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <hr />
                    <h5 class="mt-4 m-3">Conclusion</h5>
                    <p class="m-3">The Ticket Management Application is a comprehensive solution for organizations looking to manage tickets effectively. With its user-friendly design and robust functionality, it empowers teams to focus on resolving tickets promptly and improving customer satisfaction. This app is customizable to meet the unique requirements of any business.</p>
                    <hr />
                    <div>
                        <h5>Contact Information:</h5>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Email: <a href="mailto:info@voxtus.com" target="_blank" class="text-decoration-none">info@voxtus.com</a></li>
                            <li>Phone:+91-8630235507</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-3">
                <div class="mt-4 p-3" style="background-color:ghostwhite">
                    <h4 class="mt-3">Project information</h4><hr />
                    <h6 class="mt-3">Category: App Design</h6>
                    @* <h6 class="mt-3">Client: Accountable Value Financial Services</h6> *@
                    <h6 class="mt-3">Project date: 10 June, 2025</h6>
                    <h6 class="mt-3">
                        Information Technology:
                    </h6>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Power Pages</li>
                        <li>SharePoint</li>
                        <li>Power Automate</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
